<MELItem itemNbr="32-32-02" id="X-BOEING:FTID:81205.787.DDG.CU.MEL.2-32-32-02.1.2-32-32-02">
<Title>Main Gear Door Uplock Springs</Title>
<DispatchCondition repairInterval="B" nbrInstalled="4" nbrRequired="3" maintIndicator="(M)" opsIndicator="(O)">
<DispatchConditionRemarks>
<Para>One spring on one main gear uplock mechanism may be missing provided the gear extend speed placard is not exceeded.</Para>
</DispatchConditionRemarks>
<DispatchProcedure>
<MaintenanceProcedure>
<Para>Prepare the airplane for dispatch with one main gear  uplock spring missing (AMM DDG 32-32-02).</Para>
<Para>Remove any pieces of broken spring.</Para>
</MaintenanceProcedure>
<OperationProcedure>
<Para>Retract landing gear as usual, but observe the landing gear extend speed placard.</Para>
</OperationProcedure>
</DispatchProcedure>
</DispatchCondition>
</MELItem>
